<!--
  MachStruct Sparkle Appcast (P5-06)
  ===================================
  Host this file at the URL declared as SUFeedURL in Info.plist:
    https://machstruct.lustech.se/appcast.xml

  After archiving and notarizing a new release (P5-05 GitHub Actions),
  prepend a new <item> block at the top of the <channel>.

  Sign the dmgURL with:
    ./bin/sign_update /path/to/MachStruct-1.0.dmg
  (requires the EdDSA private key in your macOS keychain)
  Paste the printed sparkle:edSignature into the <enclosure> below.

  See scripts/README-sparkle.md for the full release workflow.
-->
